Package com.composum.pages.components.model.search

Class SearchResult

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.composum.pages.commons.model.AbstractModel
      • com.composum.pages.commons.model.Element
        • com.composum.pages.components.model.search.SearchResult
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    com.composum.pages.commons.model.Model, com.composum.sling.core.SlingBean
    public class SearchResult
extends com.composum.pages.commons.model.Element
    Models the possible configurations for the presentation of a search result.

    Properties selector (string); optional, default: 'searchItem' template (resourceType:renderer); optional.

    Caution: this uses the search algorithm SearchService.search(com.composum.sling.core.BeanContext, java.lang.String, java.lang.String, java.lang.String, com.composum.sling.core.filter.ResourceFilter, int, java.lang.Integer) for which there has to be aggregation configured in the lucene search (see the documentation of that method).

      • getSearchtermErrorText

        public String getSearchtermErrorText()
        A text to show when the user inputs faulty search terms. Should describe the syntax: a series of words not containing ", possibly starting with - as negated search term, or sequences of words quoted in ", possibly starting with - before the " for negation.
